<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
  <title>FL Emergency Phone</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --orange: #f26822;
      --orange-dim: rgba(242,104,34,0.12);
      --orange-border: #7a2e0a;
      --dark: #111111;
      --card: #1c1c1c;
      --card2: #222222;
      --border: #2d2d2d;
      --text: #efefef;
      --muted: #888888;
      --red: #f87171;
      --red-bg: #2a1010;
      --red-border: #7f1d1d;
      --amber: #fbbf24;
      --amber-bg: #241e08;
      --amber-border: #78350f;
      --green: #4ade80;
      --green-bg: #0b1f10;
      --green-border: #14532d;
      --blue: #93c5fd;
      --blue-bg: #0d1825;
      --blue-border: #1e3a5f;
      --mono: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
      --sans: 'IBM Plex Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--dark);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      min-height: 100dvh;
    }

    /* ===== PIN SCREEN ===== */
    #pin-screen {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100dvh;
      padding: 32px 24px;
      gap: 0;
    }

    .pin-fl {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      color: var(--orange);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .pin-wordmark {
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .pin-sub {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 44px;
    }

    .pin-dots {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .pin-dot {
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      background: transparent;
      transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
    }

    .pin-dot.filled {
      background: var(--orange);
      border-color: var(--orange);
    }

    .pin-dot.error {
      background: var(--red);
      border-color: var(--red);
    }

    .pin-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 76px);
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .pin-btn {
      width: 76px;
      height: 76px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--card);
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 22px;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: background 0.1s, border-color 0.1s, transform 0.1s;
      user-select: none;
    }

    .pin-btn:active {
      background: var(--orange);
      border-color: var(--orange);
      color: #fff;
      transform: scale(0.93);
    }

    .pin-btn.pin-del {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .pin-btn.pin-empty {
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .pin-error-msg {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--red);
      min-height: 18px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    @keyframes shake {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
      20%       { transform: translateX(-10px); }
      40%       { transform: translateX(10px); }
      60%       { transform: translateX(-7px); }
      80%       { transform: translateX(5px); }
    }

    .pin-dots.shake {
      animation: shake 0.4s ease;
    }

    /* ===== MAIN APP ===== */
    #app {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 100dvh;
    }

    /* Header */
    #app-header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 200;
      background: var(--dark);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 10px 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--orange);
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .brand-sep {
      width: 1px;
      height: 18px;
      background: var(--border);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .brand-title {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 1.2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .header-badge {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 9px;
      color: var(--red);
      border: 1px solid var(--red-border);
      background: var(--red-bg);
      padding: 2px 7px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* Emergency strip */
    #emergency-strip {
      position: sticky;
      top: 49px;
      z-index: 199;
      background: #0a0a0a;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 8px 14px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
      scrollbar-width: none;
    }

    #emergency-strip::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

    .e-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 7px 13px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      gap: 1px;
    }

    .e-btn-lbl {
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1.2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .e-btn-num {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .e-btn.e-red { background: #dc2626; color: #fff; }
    .e-btn.e-orange { background: var(--orange); color: #fff; }
    .e-btn.e-dark { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text); }

    /* Search */
    #search-wrap {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      background: var(--dark);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    #search-input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 15px;
      font-family: var(--sans);
      outline: none;
      appearance: none;
    }

    #search-input:focus { border-color: var(--orange); }
    #search-input::placeholder { color: var(--muted); }

    /* Sections */
    #sections { flex: 1; padding-bottom: 60px; }

    .section { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .section.hidden { display: none; }

    .sec-btn {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 13px 14px;
      background: transparent;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: var(--text);
      text-align: left;
      -webkit-appearance: none;
    }

    .sec-btn:active { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }

    .tier-badge {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 3px 7px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .tb-red    { background: var(--red-bg);   color: var(--red);   border: 1px solid var(--red-border); }
    .tb-amber  { background: var(--amber-bg);  color: var(--amber); border: 1px solid var(--amber-border); }
    .tb-green  { background: var(--green-bg);  color: var(--green); border: 1px solid var(--green-border); }
    .tb-blue   { background: var(--blue-bg);   color: var(--blue);  border: 1px solid var(--blue-border); }
    .tb-orange { background: #1f0e02; color: var(--orange); border: 1px solid var(--orange-border); }

    .sec-title {
      flex: 1;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    }

    .chevron {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      transition: transform 0.2s;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .section.open .chevron { transform: rotate(180deg); }

    .sec-body { display: none; padding: 2px 14px 20px; }
    .section.open .sec-body { display: block; }

    /* --- Content styles --- */
    h3 {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--orange);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin: 18px 0 8px;
    }

    h3:first-child { margin-top: 4px; }

    p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #ccc;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    .note {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Step list */
    .steps {
      list-style: none;
      counter-reset: s;
      margin: 4px 0 8px;
    }

    .steps li {
      counter-increment: s;
      display: flex;
      gap: 11px;
      margin-bottom: 11px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #ccc;
    }

    .steps li::before {
      content: counter(s);
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--orange);
      background: var(--orange-dim);
      border-radius: 50%;
      min-width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    /* Triage tiers */
    .triage-tier { border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 14px; }

    .triage-hdr {
      padding: 9px 13px;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 1.2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .tt1 .triage-hdr { background: var(--red-bg);   color: var(--red);   }
    .tt2 .triage-hdr { background: var(--amber-bg);  color: var(--amber); }
    .tt3 .triage-hdr { background: var(--green-bg);  color: var(--green); }

    .triage-item {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 3px;
      padding: 10px 13px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--card);
    }

    .triage-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .ti-sit {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .ti-act {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .ti-act strong { color: var(--text); }

    /* Contact rows */
    .crow {
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .crow:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .cname {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .cnum {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    /* Credential rows */
    .drow {
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 3px;
    }

    .drow:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .dlabel {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .dval {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--blue);
      word-break: break-all;
    }

    /* Links */
    .tel {
      color: var(--orange);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: var(--mono);
    }

    .tel:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .eml {
      color: var(--blue);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 13px;
      word-break: break-all;
    }

    .eml:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* Info boxes */
    .ibox {
      background: rgba(248,113,113,0.08);
      border: 1px solid var(--red-border);
      border-radius: 7px;
      padding: 10px 13px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #fca5a5;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .ibox.amber {
      background: rgba(251,191,36,0.07);
      border-color: var(--amber-border);
      color: #fde68a;
    }

    .ibox.blue {
      background: rgba(147,197,253,0.07);
      border-color: var(--blue-border);
      color: #bfdbfe;
    }

    .warn-bar {
      background: rgba(248,113,113,0.09);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
      padding: 9px 12px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #fca5a5;
      border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* Decision table */
    .dtable {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin: 6px 0 12px;
      border-radius: 7px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .dtable td {
      padding: 9px 11px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      vertical-align: top;
      line-height: 1.45;
      background: var(--card);
    }

    .dtable tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .dtable td:first-child { color: var(--muted); width: 48%; }
    .dtable td.sit-red { color: #fca5a5; }
    .dtable td.sit-amber { color: #fde68a; }
    .dtable td.sit-green { color: #86efac; }

    /* Reference table */
    .rtable {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin: 6px 0;
    }

    .rtable td {
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      vertical-align: top;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: #ccc;
    }

    .rtable tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .rtable td:first-child { color: var(--orange); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; width: 90px; padding-right: 10px; }

    /* No results */
    #no-results {
      padding: 50px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      display: none;
    }

    .mono { font-family: var(--mono); }
    .divider { height: 1px; background: var(--border); margin: 12px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ===== PIN SCREEN ===== -->
<div id="pin-screen">
  <div class="pin-fl">FL</div>
  <div class="pin-wordmark">Future Learning</div>
  <div class="pin-sub">Emergency Phone · Confidential</div>

  <div class="pin-dots" id="pin-dots">
    <div class="pin-dot" id="d0"></div>
    <div class="pin-dot" id="d1"></div>
    <div class="pin-dot" id="d2"></div>
    <div class="pin-dot" id="d3"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="pin-grid">
    <button class="pin-btn" onclick="pinPress('1')">1</button>
    <button class="pin-btn" onclick="pinPress('2')">2</button>
    <button class="pin-btn" onclick="pinPress('3')">3</button>
    <button class="pin-btn" onclick="pinPress('4')">4</button>
    <button class="pin-btn" onclick="pinPress('5')">5</button>
    <button class="pin-btn" onclick="pinPress('6')">6</button>
    <button class="pin-btn" onclick="pinPress('7')">7</button>
    <button class="pin-btn" onclick="pinPress('8')">8</button>
    <button class="pin-btn" onclick="pinPress('9')">9</button>
    <button class="pin-btn pin-empty" disabled aria-hidden="true"></button>
    <button class="pin-btn" onclick="pinPress('0')">0</button>
    <button class="pin-btn pin-del" onclick="pinDelete()">⌫</button>
  </div>

  <div class="pin-error-msg" id="pin-err"></div>
</div>

<!-- ===== MAIN APP ===== -->
<div id="app" hidden>

  <header id="app-header">
    <div class="brand">
      <span class="brand-mark">FL</span>
      <div class="brand-sep"></div>
      <span class="brand-title">Emergency Phone<br>Procedures Guide</span>
    </div>
    <span class="header-badge">Confidential</span>
  </header>

  <!-- Emergency call buttons -->
  <div id="emergency-strip">
    <a href="tel:999" class="e-btn e-red">
      <span class="e-btn-lbl">Emergency</span>
      <span class="e-btn-num">999</span>
    </a>
    <a href="tel:112" class="e-btn e-red">
      <span class="e-btn-lbl">Emergency</span>
      <span class="e-btn-num">112</span>
    </a>
    <a href="tel:0818776315" class="e-btn e-orange">
      <span class="e-btn-lbl">TUSLA OOH</span>
      <span class="e-btn-num">0818 776 315</span>
    </a>
    <a href="tel:0871037744" class="e-btn e-dark">
      <span class="e-btn-lbl">Emergency Phone</span>
      <span class="e-btn-num">087 103 7744</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Search -->
  <div id="search-wrap">
    <input
      type="search"
      id="search-input"
      placeholder="Search procedures, contacts, scenarios…"
      oninput="handleSearch(this.value)"
      autocomplete="off"
      autocorrect="off"
      autocapitalize="off"
      spellcheck="false"
    >
  </div>

  <!-- Accordion Sections -->
  <main id="sections">

    <!-- TRIAGE -->
    <div class="section open" data-s="triage tier 1 2 3 immediate tonight tomorrow act emergency missing child protection fire self-harm curfew arrival host family medical transfer pairing schedule complaint query">
      <button class="sec-btn" onclick="tog(this)">
        <span class="tier-badge tb-red">Triage</span>
        <span class="sec-title">Triage — Decide What To Do First</span>
        <span class="chevron">▾</span>
      </button>
      <div class="sec-body">

        <div class="triage-tier tt1">
          <div class="triage-hdr">🔴 Tier 1 — Act Immediately · Call 999 or escalate now</div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">Medical emergency — unconscious, not breathing, severe injury, anaphylaxis</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ <strong>Call <a href="tel:999" class="tel">999</a>/<a href="tel:112" class="tel">112</a>.</strong> Then notify Felipe.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">YL student missing — under 18, not located after 30 min</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ <strong>See Missing Student section.</strong> Call GL, HF, Felipe. Call 999 if risk of danger.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">Child protection concern — immediate risk of harm</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ <strong>See Child Protection section.</strong> Call 999 → Peter Lahiff → TUSLA: <a href="tel:0818776315" class="tel">0818 776 315</a></div>
          </div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">Fire or evacuation</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ <strong>See Fire &amp; Evacuation section.</strong> Call 999. Confirm all evacuated. Notify Felipe.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">Self-harm or suicidal crisis — student in immediate danger</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ <strong>See Mental Health section.</strong> Ensure someone is with student. Call 999.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="triage-tier tt2">
          <div class="triage-hdr">🟡 Tier 2 — Resolve Tonight · Needs action before morning</div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">Student not home by curfew (22:00)</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ <strong>See Curfew Breach section.</strong> Contact GL immediately.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">Arrival issue — can't find staff or transport</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ <strong>See Arrival Issues section.</strong> Check live schedule and Booking Form.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">Host family not home / not at departure</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ <strong>See Arrival Issues / Mini-Stay section.</strong> Contact HF, book taxi if needed.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">Student medical issue — urgent but not life-threatening</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ <strong>See Medical section.</strong> GP OOH contacts listed there.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">Transfer issue — taxi or bus problem</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ <strong>See Transport section.</strong> Check schedule for booking details.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="triage-tier tt3">
          <div class="triage-hdr">🟢 Tier 3 — Email &amp; Deal Tomorrow · Reassure caller, send follow-up email</div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">Request to change host family pairing</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ Cannot be actioned out of hours. Email accommodation team. See Who to Email section.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">Schedule, activity, or class queries</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ Cannot be changed out of hours. Email the relevant coordinator.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">Activity change requests from GL</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ Only possible during working hours. See Mini-Stay section.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="triage-item">
            <div class="ti-sit">Complaints or general queries</div>
            <div class="ti-act">→ Listen, reassure, email relevant manager.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CHILD PROTECTION -->
    <div class="section" data-s="child protection TUSLA peter lahiff safeguarding abuse neglect risk harm concern disclosure back-up host move under 18 designated">
      <button class="sec-btn" onclick="tog(this)">
        <span class="tier-badge tb-red">Immediate</span>
        <span class="sec-title">Child Protection</span>
        <span class="chevron">▾</span>
      </button>
      <div class="sec-body">
        <div class="ibox">The welfare and safety of the child comes first. If in any doubt, escalate — do not wait until morning.</div>

        <h3>What Constitutes a Concern</h3>
        <p>A child protection concern arises when you have reasonable grounds to believe a child (under 18) has been, is being, or is at risk of being: physically abused, emotionally abused, sexually abused, or neglected. Includes a direct disclosure, a concern raised by a GL or HF, or behaviour you observe.</p>

        <h3>What To Do — Follow In Order</h3>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>Listen carefully. Do not promise confidentiality. Do not press for details or ask leading questions.</li>
          <li>Do not confront or contact the person allegedly responsible for the harm.</li>
          <li>Ensure the student is in a safe location. If the concern involves the host family, consider activating the back-up host listed on the Booking Form.</li>
          <li>Contact <strong>Peter Lahiff</strong> immediately (number saved on phone). He is FL's designated child protection person.</li>
          <li>If child is in immediate danger and Peter is unreachable: call <a href="tel:999" class="tel">999</a>, then TUSLA out-of-hours: <a href="tel:0818776315" class="tel">0818 776 315</a>.</li>
          <li>Make a written record — what was reported, by whom, and when. Email to Peter and Felipe before ending the call.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Moving Student to Back-Up Host</h3>
        <p>The back-up host is listed on the Booking Form. Any move must be done in consultation with Peter Lahiff — not unilaterally. Alert Peter on the possibility of a TUSLA report; that decision is his to make with management.</p>

        <h3>Key Contacts</h3>
        <div class="crow">
          <div class="cname">Peter Lahiff — FL Designated Child Protection Person</div>
          <div class="cnum">Number saved on emergency phone</div>
        </div>
        <div class="crow">
          <div class="cname">TUSLA Out-of-Hours — 6pm–7am &amp; weekends / bank holidays</div>
          <div class="cnum"><a href="tel:0818776315" class="tel">0818 776 315</a></div>
        </div>
        <div class="crow">
          <div class="cname">Emergency Services — immediate risk</div>
          <div class="cnum"><a href="tel:999" class="tel">999</a> or <a href="tel:112" class="tel">112</a></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MENTAL HEALTH -->
