        <h3>Student in Emotional Distress</h3>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>Stay calm. Ask the GL or HF to stay with the student.</li>
          <li>Establish whether the student is physically safe right now.</li>
          <li>Notify Felipe by phone or message. Do not treat this as next-day if the student's safety is unclear.</li>
          <li>YL minor: the GL is responsible for the student's immediate welfare and must remain with them.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Self-Harm or Suicidal Crisis</h3>
        <div class="ibox">If a student has harmed themselves or is expressing intent to harm themselves:</div>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>Call <a href="tel:999" class="tel">999</a> immediately if the student is in immediate physical danger.</li>
          <li>Ensure someone is physically with the student at all times — do not leave them alone.</li>
          <li>Call Felipe or Peter Lahiff.</li>
          <li>Do not minimise, dismiss, or challenge what the student is saying.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Crisis Contacts</h3>
        <div class="crow">
          <div class="cname">Samaritans — 24hr, free, confidential</div>
